content: What happens after I push button that person wants to volunteer?  Do they get a call or text or what?  What if they ask me directly how to volunteer?
The script should take you to the next page to choose type of volunteer or send text, depending on the script
That hasn't happened.  Will they be contacted somehow or do I add it to the debrief form and hope they get info.
If you clicked on yes for volunteering, and there was no further script then there will be a follow up contact in the next few days
